 data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView/update":{"title":"update","abstract":[{"text":"Updates the user location annotation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView\/update","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"update","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview\/update"}}}